{"tid":232604,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔party，cdrom勿入","createTime":"2017-05-07T00:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T04:17:09.000Z","uid":555,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6716baa431673e8c3f2516406f79f81c937ec72","tid":232604,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:44:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期六，我唔去浦了。去開party。 <br />\n我地book 了麥當勞。快餐店 , 包的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/164916_e4cdf65588f83d8ca0a5e02ee89792d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F164916_e4cdf65588f83d8ca0a5e02ee89792d7.jpg&h=5c73d3d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/164915_e4cdf65588f83d8ca0a5e02ee89792d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F164915_e4cdf65588f83d8ca0a5e02ee89792d7.jpg&h=bf3a6473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐40人的。 <br />\n<br />\n仲有, McNugget 麥樂雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84w57Ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84w57Ac.jpg&h=1ebccf9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/193940_f5e34afa06bd39a862155d7a488d498d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F193940_f5e34afa06bd39a862155d7a488d498d.jpg&h=eee86b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.techorz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/mcdonalds-hk-18-chicken-mcnuggets-back-with-line-friends-packing-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.techorz.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fmcdonalds-hk-18-chicken-mcnuggets-back-with-line-friends-packing-1.jpg&h=eb5079cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，一啖過好食d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一款 脆香雞翼。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/195329_a72677516a3c4c51ebc8e5854160f9e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F195329_a72677516a3c4c51ebc8e5854160f9e7.jpg&h=350f843e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞手會搞遊戲同比賽。 <br />\n<br />\n星期六 , 7點半金鐘海富中心麥當勞集合 <br />\n<br />\n巴打：免費 <br />\n靚絲打：免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通絲打：免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d夠勇氣出黎食雞的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d party無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/t2567811q110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ft2567811q110.jpg&h=b54d03ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b3e1bcd88a4a564e06100643f5c5fc3eb4a40a8","tid":232604,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:48:14.000Z","msg":"應該係毒撚勿入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78ea375a69ec48aa22ca05afb727bd09bdfbee0","tid":232604,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:50:23.000Z","msg":"好野 又有得去識老泥mk妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1192f1be254c80cf7f34a5e2b7aa1af61f85f37c","tid":232604,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係毒撚勿入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁最尾張圖果班咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bf671a4d6d71fa809926b764202775fd982231","tid":232604,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"好多00後"},{"pid":"baf1d3922b59fc064354a76b3946e638dc046292","tid":232604,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係毒撚勿入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /